        <updateDate>2026-02-25T16:53:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>COVID Fraud Transparency Act of 2025</strong></p><p>This bill requires the Small Business Administration's Office of Inspector General to report quarterly about fraud cases involving certain COVID-19 loans (e.g., Paycheck Protection Program loans).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
